data.text: Don’t make the mistake like me and “nurse” the arm by not moving it. The uncomfortable feeling the first day will get much worse.

I would like to add an update on this for anyone who gets it and reads this, even if it helps one person.

Have it injected in the arm of your non-dominant hand. The vaccine will be a little uncomfortable the first day; but, the trick is to continue moving that arm. Constantly.
